138
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:46,965
Topiku? Oh, topiku…

139
00:08:47,048 --> 00:08:48,174
[petugas 4] Dasar kau, bocah nakal!

140
00:08:48,258 --> 00:08:50,885
-Berbaring di tanah!
-[tentara] Berbaring di tanah!

141
00:08:52,011 --> 00:08:55,306
Pada nomor satu, "Aturan berpakaian."
Pada nomor dua, "Pelanggaran." Satu!

142
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:56,516
[semua] Aturan berpakaian!

143
00:08:56,599 --> 00:08:58,476
-Dua!
-Pelanggaran!

144
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,645
-Satu!
-Aturan berpakaian!

145
00:09:00,728 --> 00:09:02,897
-Dua!
-Pelanggaran!

146
00:09:02,981 --> 00:09:04,107
-Satu!
-Aturan berpakaian!

147
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:05,191
[Dokter] Tidak mungkin.

148
00:09:06,067 --> 00:09:07,986
Tidak mungkin aku akan berakhir di sebuah pulau.

149
00:09:08,695 --> 00:09:10,864
Aku tidak mungkin sesial itu.

150
00:09:17,704 --> 00:09:18,830
SAYA…

151
00:09:19,497 --> 00:09:20,707
Itu sungguh sial.

152
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:22,167
