153
00:09:22,250 --> 00:09:23,626
TRANSPORTASI KELAUTAN YEOPOONG

154
00:09:23,710 --> 00:09:29,007
EPISODE 1
DOKTER YANG DIKIRIM KE PULAU

155
00:09:29,632 --> 00:09:32,177
Wow, beneran? Oke.

156
00:09:32,844 --> 00:09:34,846
Kurasa aku harus pergi.

157
00:09:37,974 --> 00:09:39,601
Aku benar-benar tidak yakin bisa melakukan ini.

158
00:09:39,684 --> 00:09:42,187
Sungguh, aku rasa aku benar-benar tidak bisa pergi.

159
00:09:43,021 --> 00:09:44,564
Kau harus pergi, bodoh.

160
00:09:44,647 --> 00:09:46,024
Apa lagi yang bisa kamu lakukan?

161
00:09:48,693 --> 00:09:49,694
Oh, astaga…

162
00:09:50,195 --> 00:09:53,198
[telepon berdering]

163
00:09:58,786 --> 00:09:59,787
Hei, Gangseok.

164
00:09:59,871 --> 00:10:01,122
Apakah kamu akan pergi sekarang?

165
00:10:01,206 --> 00:10:02,415
[Dokter] Ya.

166
00:10:02,498 --> 00:10:03,750
Kamu akan mengalami masa-masa sulit.

167
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:06,711
-Bagaimana dengan obatmu?
-Belum.

168
00:10:06,794 --> 00:10:09,756
Obat-obatan tersebut dapat menyebabkan efek samping
seperti kehilangan memori, pusing,

169
