179
00:10:40,578 --> 00:10:43,373
Jika kau khawatir dengan bekas lukaku,
tutup mulutmu dan buka dompetmu.

180
00:10:44,290 --> 00:10:46,376
-[Gangseok] Halo? Jiui.
-Ya.

181
00:10:46,459 --> 00:10:48,461
-Semoga berhasil di sana.
-Terima kasih, Gangseok.

182
00:10:48,544 --> 00:10:49,545
Tentu.

183
00:10:50,672 --> 00:10:52,465
[bunyi klakson kapal]

184
00:10:53,925 --> 00:10:55,510
