189
00:11:29,127 --> 00:11:33,381
Kapal yang menuju Pyeongdongdo,
Pyeongdongdo kini sedang berangkat.

190
00:11:33,965 --> 00:11:36,092
Semua penumpang yang tersisa…

191
00:11:40,471 --> 00:11:42,473
[audio terdistorsi]

192
00:11:50,481 --> 00:11:52,483
[bernapas berat]

193
00:11:55,486 --> 00:11:56,821
Silakan…

194
00:11:58,364 --> 00:11:59,615
[terengah-engah]

195
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:03,328
DO JI UI, M
ELLMARP

196
00:12:10,043 --> 00:12:11,586
[Jiui, normal] Dua jam ke Pyeongdongdo.

197
00:12:14,964 --> 00:12:16,382
Yang perlu saya lakukan hanyalah tertidur.

198
00:12:17,675 --> 00:12:19,093
Tidak akan terjadi apa-apa.

199
00:12:20,136 --> 00:12:21,220
Tidak ada apa-apa.
STYLE
