202
00:12:55,421 --> 00:12:57,006
[penumpang 1] Kita perlu meluruskan
angka-angka kita.

203
00:12:57,090 --> 00:12:58,424
Permisi, anak muda.

204
00:12:58,508 --> 00:12:59,509
Hei, anak muda.

205
00:12:59,592 --> 00:13:01,094
Hei, buka matamu.

206
00:13:01,803 --> 00:13:03,888
[penumpang 2] Anak muda!

207
00:13:03,971 --> 00:13:07,183
Ada sesuatu yang ingin kami tanyakan kepada Anda.

208
00:13:07,266 --> 00:13:09,310
[suara teredam] Temanku ini
tidak punya uang tunai,

209
00:13:09,394 --> 00:13:12,105
